- ProductImageCarousel - A collection view that contains medium sized product images.
- SKUDrawer - A drawer that slides in/out with available SKUs.
- ProductInfoSlab - Contains the product's name, any special discounts or event related info about the product (holiday, etc.)
- ProductActionSlab - Contains all actions that can be performed on the shopping cart / reservation / wishlist.
- ProductReviewSlab - Contains an image with stars that can be expanded to show first 3 reviews of product.
- SuggestedProductsCarousel X 2 - A carousel that provides related/suggested/recommended products with an image and the product's name.
- PolicyLinksSlab - Provides links to our privacy policy, copyright, etc.